00:33:01,680 --> 00:33:03,432
AII right. sir. Here we go.

524
00:33:07,040 --> 00:33:09,111
Oswald! My friend.

525
00:33:09,800 --> 00:33:12,110
Bruce Wayne? What a lovely surprise.

526
00:33:12,480 --> 00:33:15,154
You certainly are getting out
