527
00:33:15,320 --> 00:33:17,994
The way I see it, everyone else
in this town is having fun.

528
00:33:18,080 --> 00:33:20,117
- Why shouldn't I?
- I agree.

529
00:33:20,400 --> 00:33:22,437
You and your insanely large
bank account

530
00:33:22,560 --> 00:33:23,880
are more than welcome here.

531
00:33:24,080 --> 00:33:25,080
- Ha!
- (PENGUIN CHUCKLES)

532
00:33:25,960 --> 00:33:27,189
Barbara Kean.

533
00:33:28,360 --> 00:33:29,873
I thought she died.

534
00:33:30,840 --> 00:33:33,070
Unfortunately, nobody stays dead
in this town.

535
00:33:34,680 --> 00:33:35,954
Excuse me.

536
00:33:37,040 --> 00:33:38,633
You do realize, don't you,
Master Bruce,

537
00:33:38,720 --> 00:33:40,119
that if you actually win.

538
00:33:40,640 --> 00:33:42,358
Ra's al Ghul
will come after the knife.

539
00:33:45,440 --> 00:33:46,669
Let him.

540
00:33:46,760 --> 00:33:50,390
The next item up for auction
is an embalming knife.

541
00:33:50,920 --> 00:33:54,151
From the tomb of
King Balahsi of Sumeria.

542
00:33:55,040 --> 00:33:57,395
