543
00:33:58,240 --> 00:34:00,754
A hundred thousand dollars.

544
00:34:01,280 --> 00:34:02,360
What does she want with it?

545
00:34:02,560 --> 00:34:04,153
I have no idea.

546
00:34:04,520 --> 00:34:05,669
Stay focused.

547
00:34:05,760 --> 00:34:07,512
One hundred thousand dollars
to Ms. Kean.

548
00:34:07,720 --> 00:34:11,475
- Do I hear...
- One hundred thousand and one dollar.

549
00:34:11,800 --> 00:34:14,553
