00:41:58,720 --> 00:41:59,915
I'm impressed.

686
00:42:00,760 --> 00:42:02,034
I had a good teacher.

687
00:42:03,520 --> 00:42:04,999
I wish you'd have called ahead.

688
00:42:09,200 --> 00:42:11,191
Does that mean
you don't have the knife?

689
00:42:12,320 --> 00:42:14,152
No. Bruce Wayne has it.

690
00:42:15,200 --> 00:42:16,349
Bruce?

691
00:42:17,280 --> 00:42:18,395
Really?

692
00:42:20,280 --> 00:42:21,509
How interesting.

693
00:42:23,640 --> 00:42:25,597
- Y0u're not angry?
- No. Not at all.

694
00:42:25,680 --> 00:42:27,034
You see, Barbara,

695
00:42:27,120 --> 00:42:29,316
when I bathed you in the Lazarus Pit.

696
00:42:29,800 --> 00:42:32,076
I did it in the knowledge that
you would become

697
00:42:32,360 --> 00:42:33,919
a competent ally of mine.

698
00:42:34,400 --> 00:42:35,595
And so far,

699
00:42:35,920 --> 00:42:37,593
you've done an admirable job.

700
00:42:41,000 --> 00:42:43,435
I'm glad you feel that way.

701
00:42:44,840 --> 00:42:46,672
And I wouldn't worry
about that knife.

702
00:42:48,280 --> 00:42:49,839
Didn't seem all that special to me.

703
00:42:51,280 --> 00:42:53,590
Oh, but you couldn't be more wrong.

704
00:42:54,200 --> 00:42:55,270
You see,

705
00:42:56,080 --> 00:42:57,229
that knife

706
00:42:58,040 --> 00:42:59,439
is the key

707
00:42:59,880 --> 00:43:01,473
to everything.

708
00:43:04,880 --> 00:43:06,632
Well, not everything.

